import numpy as np

def calculate_interquartile_range(numeric_sequences):
    iqr_values = []
    for sequence in numeric_sequences:
        q1 = np.percentile(sequence, 25)
        q3 = np.percentile(sequence, 75)
        iqr = q3 + q1
        iqr_values.append(iqr)
    return iqr_values
